                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 6va: Record concerning the gathering of the monks to prohibit the selling of the monastery's books. </locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 6va: Gathered in the church, teachers and all priest and masters of Däbrä Dammo said (the following) because they heard that foolish men sold many old books having taken them down from the mountain. Because of this they said, "We condemn and excommunicate with our word that this book may not leave the gate of the church". And furthermore they said, "The one who stole this book or erased (its text) or took it down from the mountain or brought it out from the gate of the church except for looking or reading inside shall be excommunicated by the authority of the word of our lords Peter and Paul and by the word of our father ˀArägawi and by the word of our Lady, Holy Virgin Mary, mother of our Saviour". </q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 12rb-va: Excerpt from the Mäṣḥafä śərˁat, Introductory rite of al-Muˁallaqah.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 12rb: ወያንብቡ፡ ዘንተ፡ ትእዛዘ፡ እምቅድመ፡ አንብቦ፡ ተአምር፡ በኵሉ፡ እኁድ፡ ወበኵሉ፡ በዓላቲሃ፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ። ከመ፡ ኢይምሰሎሙ፡ ለክ[ር]ስቲያን፡ ቀሊለ፡ ሰሚዓ፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ እስመ፡ ዓቢይ፡ ወክቡር፡ ውእቱ።  ...</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 174rc: Donation note.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 174rc: ለዛቲ: ተአምር፡ አጽሐፍክዋ፡ በንዋይየ። አነ፡ ወልደ፡ አረጋዊ፡ ረድኡ፡ ለአቡነ፡ ማትያስ። ወወሀብክዋ፡ ለመቅደሰ፡ አቡየ፡ አረጋዊ፡ ዘደብረ፡ ዳሞ። ከመ፡ ትኩነኒ፡ ዓራቂተ፡ ምስለ፡ አምላኪየ፡ ኄር። እምጣነ፡ አልብየ፡ አሐቲ፡ ምግባረ፡ ሠናይ። ለክሙኒ፡ ኦአበውየ፡ ወአኃውየ፡ በእንተ፡ እግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ እስእለክሙ፡ በፍቅር፡ መንፈሳዊ።  ከመ፡ ኢትርስኡኒ፡ በሕይወትየ፡ ወበሞትየ። እስመ፡ አልብየ፡ ዘመድ፡ ዘእንበሌክሙ፡ ወተአምሩ፡ አንትሙ፡ ከመ፡ የዓቢ፡ እኅው፡ መንፈሳዊ። እምነ፡ እኅው፡ ሥጋዊ። </q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The title ተአምረ፡ ማርያም and the internal number of the monastic library (338) are written on fol. 1r together with two short notes: ዝተአምር፡ ዘደብረ፡ ዳሞ፡ መካነ፡ አቡነ፡ አረጋዊ፡ "This is the (book of) miracles of Däbrä Dammo, the place of ʾabunä ʾArägawi" and ተአምር፡ ዘእግዝእትነ፡ ማርየም "Miracles of Our Lady Mary".&#xD;
- Musical notation: fols. 11rb-12rb.&#xD;
- A secondary hand has added to some supplication: ወምስለ፡ ኵልነ፡ አግብርቲሃ "and with all of us, her servants" (fols. 18ra, 19vb, 29rc, 58va) or ወምስሌነሂ "and also with us" (fols. 20vc, 23va).&#xD;
&#xD;
- Erasures are marked with thin lines: e.g., fols. 9vb, 25rb, 49ra, 51vb, 57rc, 67ra, 76ra, 90vc, 93rc, 110vb, 112vc, 113rab, 117rc, 120rb, 124vab, 149rb, 154rb, 161va, 162rb, 170vb, 173vc. &#xD;
- Thin lines are used to fill the line: fols. 65rb, 68vb, 69rc, 92ra-vc, 158ra (at the end of several lines).&#xD;
- Omissions are inserted interlineally: fols. 9ra, 10va, 43ra, 53vc, 55vb, 57rc, 57vb, 70ra, 71rc, 72rc, 92rc, 93rc, 114va, 120rb, 120va, 126vc, 129va, 132rb, 142vb, 143vb, 148rb (in red), 152va, 159rb (in red), 160ra, 163vc.&#xD;
- Omitted incipit of one miracle is written in the upper margin on fol. 90r.&#xD;
- Corrections are written over erasures: fols. 112vb, 170rc.&#xD;
- Pen trial, mentioning Tuesday: fol. 177v.</item>
