                     <origDate notBefore="1772" notAfter="1772" instant="false">According to the colophon, the Ms. was written in the third year of the reign of King Täklä Haymanot who is King Täklä Haymanot II (r. 1769-77), put on the throne by ras Mikaʾel Sǝhul on 17 October 1769. Ras Mikaʾel is also mentioned in the colophon.&#xD;
