      <profileDesc>
         <particDesc default="false">
            <listPerson default="false">
               <person instant="false"><!--donor-->
                  <persName corresp="PRS0000" instant="false" full="yes">According to Additio 3, the Ms. was donated by Wäldä ʾArägawi, disciple of ʾabunä Matǝyas. Both names are mentioned in supplication formulas, sometimes written interlineally in the main hand. In addition, further names were added to supplication formulas by the main hand: his father Zä-Wäldä Maryam (fols. 19vc, 25ra, 32rc etc.) and his mother ʾAmätä Krǝstos (fols. 22vc, 25rc etc.).</persName>
